#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

// #taxon[Taxon]
#title[Equivalence of Species of Types]

An _equivalence_ of species is a pointwise equivalence of types. In symbols: For species $F : Uu_1 -> Uu_2$ and $G: Uu_1 -> Uu_3$ we define the type of equivalences as
$
 "equiv-species-types" := Pi_(X: Uu_1) F(X) = F(Y).
$
